data.description: Attractively designed 2 bedroom, 2 bath NE ranch villa with bright and airy sunroom. Foyer with coat closet. Enjoy the great room with unique ceiling line and wall of Andersen windows. The kitchen is complete with raised panel oak cabinetry, breakfast bar, stainless appliances (not warranted) and newer GRANITE counters. Ample dining area that leads to the 4 season sunroom with great windows. Extra storage in the walk-in laundry with large pantry and  utility closet.  The primary en suite has a very large walk-in closet and over sized shower. Arched 2 panel painted doors. Newer luxury vinyl plank flooring. Huge outdoor space with extended patio that backs to private tree line. Villa services include: mowing, fertilizing, mulching, trimming front landscape and snow removal.
